==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: mailing
<hw>mail"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
or process of sending materials through the mail.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A quantity of mail, such as letters, magazines,
advertising brochures, etc., sent at one time by one person or
organization; <as>as, the ads with coupons will go out in our next
<ex>mailing</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>mailing address</ent>⟦br⟧
